p.d: Born in Calgary, Tegan and Sara began their musical path in 1995 and at the age of 26 have released 5 albums. Tegan currently resides in Vancouver, BC and Sara resides in Montreal, QC. Tegan and Sara released their fifth album, THE CON, on July 24, 2007. Immerse yourself in their incredible performance, live at the Enmore Theatre, in Sydney, Australia.
